OL,6,FThe granting of bail to one of the men
OL,7,Fcharged with the attempted murder of
OL,8,FDetective Chief Inspector John
OL,9,FCaldwell is to be overturned, a High
OL,10,FCourt judge ruled today.
OL,12,FMr Justice O'Hara held that 48-year-
OL,13,Fold Alan McFarland must remain in
OL,14,Fcustody over his alleged role in the
OL,15,Fbid to kill the off-duty PSNI officer
OL,16,Fin Omagh, Co Tyrone.
