OL,6,FHe said: "I believe, based on what has
OL,7,Fbeen outlined to me on behalf of the
OL,8,Fprosecution, that he was actively
OL,9,Finvolved in the events immediately
OL,10,Faround the time that DCI Caldwell's
OL,11,Flife was attacked.
OL,13,F"An individual as apparently committed
OL,14,Fto murder as that cannot expect to get
OL,15,Fbail."
OL,17,FProsecutors mounted the successful
OL,18,Fappeal after a magistrate initially
OL,19,Fdecided on Tuesday that McFarland, of
OL,20,FDeverney Park in Omagh, could be
OL,21,Freleased on strict terms.
