OL,6,FDCI Caldwell was shot and seriously
OL,7,Fwounded in front of his son just after
OL,8,Fhe had finished coaching a youth
OL,9,Ffootball team at sports facilities in
OL,10,Fthe town on February 22 last year.
OL,12,FTwo men wearing dark waterproof
OL,13,Fclothing approached him and opened
OL,14,Ffire, striking him several times.
OL,16,FThe gunmen made their getaway in a
OL,17,FFord Fiesta, fitted with false number
OL,18,Fplates and discovered burnt out later
OL,19,Fthat night, before switching to a
OL,20,FMercedes car.
