OL,6,FAlthough the New IRA claimed
OL,7,Fresponsibility for the shooting,
OL,8,Fdetectives believe other criminal
OL,9,Ffactions joined forces with the
OL,10,Fdissident republican grouping to
OL,11,Ftarget someone regarded as their joint
OL,12,Fenemy.
OL,14,FIt was also revealed in court there
OL,15,Fhad been a prior bid to kill DCI
OL,16,FCaldwell in an attack planned for
OL,17,Fthree weeks earlier.
