OL,6,FMcFarland is one of eight men charged
OL,7,Fwith his attempted murder. He was
OL,8,Fallegedly involved in the acquisition
OL,9,Fof one of the cars used in the
OL,10,Fassassination plot.
OL,12,FThe court heard McFarland had been
OL,13,Fpresent at an auction house in
OL,14,FBallyclare, Co Antrim on February 8
OL,15,Fwhen another suspect purchased the
OL,16,FFord Fiesta.
OL,18,FDuring the auction event he received a
OL,19,Fphone call from 33-year-old co-accused
OL,20,FMatthew McClean, from Glenpark Road in
OL,21,FOmagh.
