OL,9,Fcircumstantial case against McFarland
OL,10,Frelates to forensic swabs taken when
OL,11,Fhe was initially arrested on the day
OL,12,Fafter the shooting.
OL,14,FParticles characteristic of Cartridge
OL,15,FDischarge Residue were found on his
OL,16,Fhand and jacket pocket, according to
OL,17,Fthe prosecution.
