OL,6,FMr Justice O'Hara was also told there
OL,7,Fis information that he knew about DCI
OL,8,FCaldwell's regular movements - in
OL,9,Fparticular the night he attended the
OL,10,FYouth Sports complex where the
OL,11,Fshooting took place.
OL,13,FDefence counsel confirmed McFarland
OL,14,Fdenies any role in the murder bid. He
OL,15,Fargued that the accused had given
OL,16,Fpolice access to his phone and
OL,17,Fprovided a statement disavowing any
OL,18,Fassociation with dissident republican
OL,19,Fterrorists.
