OL,6,FWith McFarland previously questioned
OL,7,Fand released as part of the
OL,8,Finvestigation, it was contended that
OL,9,Fhis presence at the auction when the
OL,10,FFiesta was purchased "tipped the
OL,11,Fbalance" in the subsequent decision to
OL,12,Fcharge him.
OL,14,FBut the court heard he regularly
OL,15,Fattended those sales, had a long-term
OL,16,Ffriendship with McClean based on their
OL,17,Fshared interest in cars, and that the
OL,18,Fpair had been in phone contact up to
OL,19,F1,200 times in the previous four
OL,20,Fmonths.
