OL,6,FCounsel argued that the only new
OL,7,Fevidence raised during McFarland's
OL,8,Fsecond set of police interviews
OL,9,Frelated to the auctions in Ballyclare.
OL,11,FBased on the evidence, however, Mr
OL,12,FJustice O'Hara held that his alleged
OL,13,Frole was more significant than other
OL,14,Faccused who have been granted bail.
OL,16,FHe added: "The context of this case is
OL,17,Fsinister in the extreme. "Dissident
OL,18,Frepublicans combining with non-
OL,19,Fpolitical criminals to (attempt to)
OL,20,Fmurder a senior police officer."
